{"tid":541186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【常識都唔知？】強國男機艙食煙罰$1.2萬 強辯無中文廣播","createTime":"2018-01-26T07:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T12:35:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7317a24153863347ea155b22afa51856235151","tid":541186,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180126/large/1516946776_b076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180126%2Flarge%2F1516946776_b076.jpg&h=fdb147a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信飛機上全面禁煙是常識吧，但有中國旅客卻以「不知道」為由，在機上吸煙，昨日最終被罰上逾萬元。<br />\n<br />\n昨日，雲南一名李姓男子（41歲）承認，本月16日在一班從馬來西亞吉隆坡第二國際機場飛往斗湖的亞洲航空（AirAsia，簡稱亞航）AK5746航班上的廁所內吸煙。<br />\n<br />\n該案的主控官黛央諾阿扎麗娜瓦蒂認為，被告的行為危害到其他乘客的安全，為了公眾利益，需要以儆效尤。<br />\n<br />\n被告的代表律師則認為，由於被告首次搭乘飛機出國，在飛往斗湖的行程中，被告對禁煙一事毫不知情，而且沒有這方面的中文廣播。<br />\n<br />\n李男最終被判罰款6,000令吉（約1.22萬港元），若無法繳付罰款，則以入獄3個月代替。李男在繳付罰款後，即交由移民局跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180126/57756388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180126%2F57756388&d=1VqxJALpQ4PnxmeZzgJjrpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=f854aba0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180126%2F57756388&h=7c7b82aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180126/57756388</a>"},{"pid":"a666336f8b52c99fe809a0da756ac358dee64209","tid":541186,"uid":13724,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"圖都唔明? 弱智？"},{"pid":"62b39319d4a1700b178ce0204f268740def103c1","tid":541186,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"文化差異"},{"pid":"90e81461e35f83986b0979002bc98589fc7660c0","tid":541186,"uid":11962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:40:04.000Z","msg":"民智未開係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d10fffa1f2a69c88f5e53941c5792a7ff8a258","tid":541186,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"爺有的時錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e4d18ae056c3b978e861746a2d9beaf0ef5d1a","tid":541186,"uid":3706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"需要以儆效尤<br />\n<br />\n罰咁少就夠？"},{"pid":"b8eacb0544e7535d260f755126b0b40890a9041c","tid":541186,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"只係駁嘴 根本有咩可能唔知 文化低既人 自制係差啲"},{"pid":"08995610f27c773c31742df50045c9d026907015","tid":541186,"uid":164928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:38:56.000Z","msg":"咩叫顯世？<br />\n這是個好例子"},{"pid":"ead8e2183993b27300d1094e0c68d541f3c5b53f","tid":541186,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議支那人杯葛亞航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"651a52eee6348c4c40c55950af9c6f667abbd5f4","tid":541186,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"咁佢去吉隆坡程機有冇食到？"},{"pid":"35c141400c8d2d29cfc06f16473e475f8e0b7662","tid":541186,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"好彩罰到<br />\n好嘢"}]}